@host = http://localhost:5299

### Place an order (happy path — prod-1 is seeded with 100 units)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-001",
  "items": [
    { "productId": "prod-1", "productName": "Widget", "quantity": 2, "unitPrice": 9.99 }
  ]
}

###

### Place an order that will fail — product does not exist
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-002",
  "items": [
    { "productId": "no-such-product", "productName": "Ghost Item", "quantity": 1, "unitPrice": 5.00 }
  ]
}

###

### Place an order that will fail — quantity exceeds stock
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "cust-003",
  "items": [
    { "productId": "prod-1", "productName": "Widget", "quantity": 999, "unitPrice": 9.99 }
  ]
}

###

### Get order status — replace {id} with an order ID from a POST response above
GET {{host}}/api/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json
